positive.review:
One of the most emotional and beautifully crafted games I’ve played in years. 
GOTY without a doubt 🥖
- 100+ hours.
- all achievements;
- zero boredom;
- zero skipped cutscenes;
- several emotional breakdowns (in a good way);
- music so good I pre-ordered the vinyl and can’t wait for the London concert next year.










(and yeah, f*ck Simon)
